{
  "texts": [
    "In ResNet152, modifications include not only the removal of the average pooling and fully connected layers, but also alterations to the third block of the second layer by removing its last two layers and removing the final four layers of the overall model.",
    "For VGG16, the last twelve layers are omitted, capturing more primitive patterns.",
    "The last layer of EfficientNet-B2 is removed to maintain consistency with the modifications made to the other two models.",
    "These models, applied in parallel to the input, capture different levels of features.",
    "The custom layers comprise a Convolutional Block (ConvBlock), followed by a Parallel Squeeze-and-Excitation (P_scSE) block 52, and a dropout layer."
  ]
}